text: Carneades hemileuca is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Bates in 1881. It is known from Costa Rica and Panama.BioLib.cz - Carneades hemileuca. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1881
title: Carneades hemileuca
